sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant KServe as KServe/ModelMesh<br/>InferenceService
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMES as LMES Controller
    participant EvalPod as LMEval Pod
    participant Driver as ta-lmes-driver<br/>18080/TCP localhost
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GORCH as GORCH Controller
    participant Orch as Orchestrator Pod
    participant EH as EvalHub Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant MLFlow as MLFlow<br/>HTTPS

    Note over Client,TAS: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Payload Processing
    Client->>Router: POST /api<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Router->>KRBP: Forward<br/>8443/TCP TLS (reencrypt)
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview
    KRBP->>TAS: Forward<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    TAS-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Client: Response
    KServe->>KRBP: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>8443/TCP TLS (serving cert)
    Note right of KServe: MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS env

    Note over Client,OCI: Flow 2: LMEvalJob Execution
    Client->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>LMES: Watch notification
    LMES->>K8sAPI: Create Pod<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS SA token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalPod: Pod created
    Note over EvalPod: Init container copies driver binary
    EvalPod->>Driver: Start driver process
    Driver->>S3: Download assets (if offline)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS AWS IAM
    S3-->>Driver: Model/dataset artifacts
    Driver->>Driver: Run lm-evaluation-harness
    LMES->>Driver: GET /GetStatus (pod exec)<br/>18080/TCP HTTP localhost
    Driver-->>LMES: Status + progress
    Driver->>OCI: Upload results (if configured)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Basic auth
    Driver->>Driver: Write results to PVC
    LMES->>K8sAPI: Update LMEvalJob status

    Note over GORCH,Orch: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestrator Auto-Discovery
    GORCH->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS SA token
    K8sAPI-->>GORCH: InferenceService list
    GORCH->>K8sAPI: List Services by label<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS SA token
    K8sAPI-->>GORCH: Detector services
    GORCH->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ConfigMaps<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS SA token
    Note over GORCH: Generate orchestrator config
    Orch->>KServe: Forward to InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/HTTP TLS
    Orch->>Orch: Apply detector guardrails

    Note over Client,MLFlow: Flow 4: EvalHub Evaluation & Monitoring
    Client->>Router: API request<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Router->>EH: Forward<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (reencrypt)
    Note over EH: SAR with X-Tenant scoping
    EH->>DB: Query/store data<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    DB-->>EH: Results
    EH->>MLFlow: Experiment tracking<br/>HTTPS TLS (service CA)
    Note over EH: Projected SA token auth
    MLFlow-->>EH: Tracking response
    EH-->>Router: API response
    Router-->>Client: Response
